title: The Clash Sold Out! Merch Tee
body_html: Introducing The Clash - protest, rebellion and brilliant punk rock. One of the most explosive bands in history was well deserving of a tee with impact. Matching their rough and raw reputation is a poster style, drapey tee with a black and white print of the group made to feel like an old photo find. Accented in red lettering with their star logo and name on the back. Its oversized fit and monochrome style make it easy to wear with whatever you got going on.THE SPECSMade from a 100% cotton fabric, feels like a luxury tour shirt with the perfect drapeA blend of our Weekend Tee and OS Tee, this tee is meant to fit like that perfect vintage tee find.
